---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy — Community Starter"
  description="Community Starter privacy information."
>
  <article class="page-heading reading cs-shell">
    <p class="cs-eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Your information has a purpose, an owner, and an end.</h1>
    <p>
      Optional processing is disabled until you choose it. Community data is
      scoped to current access, and account holders can correct, export,
      deactivate, or request deletion of their data.
    </p>
    <p>
      This starter must be specialized with an accountable privacy owner before
      launch.
    </p>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
